{"tid":1032495,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：大灣區執教供教師多一個選擇","createTime":"2019-02-22T11:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T12:14:42.000Z","uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3be669bfd378c6a5e45c0b7d7d44cc625c9594ca","tid":1032495,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=338481&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338481%26refer%3D&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLdXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=2cd29c99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338481%26refer%3D&h=a03866b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=338481&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄：大灣區執教供教師多一個選擇<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】粵港澳大灣區規劃綱要提出，研究開放港澳教師到廣東考取資格並任教。教育局局長楊潤雄表示，正跟內地商討細節。他承認香港教師薪酬較高，安排是為有志在內地執教的教師提供多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n至於政府曾探討本港辦學團體到大灣區辦香港課程的學校，讓日後到大灣區工作的港人的子女入讀，以便銜接本地課程，楊潤雄指，仍跟內地政府及本港的辦學團體商討政策及資源上的配合。"},{"pid":"b63bfe338ce67f2ec6a5328dc2e45cbf917229b0","tid":1032495,"uid":49222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:02:46.000Z","msg":"大灣區性愛供地方媽媽多一個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d9e08bbe2abdd518beb076ccac84f94f740b82","tid":1032495,"uid":103230,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:05:06.000Z","msg":"安排是為有志在內地執教的教師提供多一個選擇。<br />\n<br />\n講出黎面唔面紅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工差兩倍以上<br />\n有邊個會想上去教書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d31b639a8741f9d1ddd854b2a55d08dd9824cc","tid":1032495,"uid":6604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T12:05:16.000Z","msg":"連登某會員喺雨傘運動結束一年都未夠<br />\n就身先士卒上大灣區作育英才<br />\n春風化雨<br />\n好有前瞻性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" c